These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, baking
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading | skydiving   | baking |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, italian
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, turtle
1. the malaysian is somewhere between the italian and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the italian##3
3. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the malaysian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian   | egyptian   |
| Pet        | rat | turtle | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, dog
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, subway
1. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person driving the bus##7
3. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Pet        | hedgehog | dog | cat |
| Transport   | bus       | subway     | car         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, puzzles
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | rock-climbing | singing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, time-travel
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel | adventure |
| Game           | scrabble    | monopoly      | mah-jongg  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
House: palace, gothic-revival, townhouse
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
3. the townhouse house is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| House   | gothic-revival | palace | townhouse |
| Pet   | horse        | goat   | chinchilla     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | sprite |
| Birthday        | january      | march    | september |

 #################################

 
