.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, raspberry, watermelon
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, palace
1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the person eating pear##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | pear  | raspberry |
| House   | townhouse     | gothic-revival | palace   |

