.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, singing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby   | dancing       | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | tennis     |

